<bibRefCitation author="Clark" box="[853,982,922,949]" firstAuthor="Clark" pageId="125" pageNumber="126" refId="ref177414" refString="Clark, H. L. (1925) A catalogue of the Recent sea urchins (Echinoidea) in the British Museum (Natural History). Trustees of the British Museum and Oxford University Press, London, 250 pp." type="book" year="1925">Clark 1925</bibRefCitation>
