<bibRefCitation author="Mortensen" box="[159,361,994,1021]" firstAuthor="Mortensen" pageId="125" pageNumber="126" refId="ref193260" refString="Mortensen, T. (1951 b) A Monograph of the Echinoidea. Vol. 2. Spatangoida II. Amphisternata II. Spatangidae, Loveniidae, Pericosmidae, Schizasteridae, Brissidae. C. A. Reitzel, Copenhagen, 593 pp." type="book" year="1951" yearSuffix="b">Mortensen 1951b</bibRefCitation>
